    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and its signature individual throttle bodies. This naturally aspirated powerplant delivers a linear torque curve and an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The chassis maintains its composure through M-specific suspension geometry and a functional M-variable differential lock for optimal power distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing inspection and throttle actuator service, ensuring the longitudinal powertrain remains reliable. With hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering offering tactile feedback, this example is a purist-spec machine optimized for both canyon carving and track-day reliability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
